episodes.title: John Travolta Explains Scientology's Silent Births | Friday Night With Jonathan Ross
episodes.description:
John Travolta joins Jonathan on the couch to talk Scientology and relive his Oscar-nominated successes, after, Ricky Gervais and Travolta bond by sharing a disco moment, with John reprising his Seventies dance moves and Ricky revamping his equally iconic sequence from The Office.
